## Permissions (constants.ts)

**For CRUD operations (most entities), use CrudPermissionDefinition:**

```typescript
import { CrudPermissionDefinition } from '@vendure/core';

export const myEntityPermission = new CrudPermissionDefinition('MyEntity');
// Generates: myEntityPermission.Create, .Read, .Update, .Delete
```

**For single-action operations, use PermissionDefinition:**

```typescript
import { PermissionDefinition } from '@vendure/core';

export const myPermission = new PermissionDefinition({
    name: 'MyAction',
    description: 'Allows performing MyAction',
});
// Usage: myPermission.Permission
```

