## Import Conventions

- Vendure core imports: `from '@vendure/core'`
- TypeORM decorators: `from 'typeorm'`
- NestJS decorators: `from '@nestjs/common'` and `from '@nestjs/graphql'`
- GraphQL tag: `from 'graphql-tag'`
- Admin types (codegen): `from '../../../codegen/adminTypes'` (relative path from resolver)
- Shop types (codegen): `from '../../../codegen/shopTypes'`

---

## Checklist for New Plugin

- [ ] Plugin directory created under `src/plugins/<name>/`
- [ ] Entity file(s) created with proper decorators
- [ ] Translation entity created (if translatable)
- [ ] Constants file with permission definition
- [ ] Service with CRUD operations
- [ ] Admin resolver with permissions
- [ ] Shop resolver (if public data)
- [ ] GraphQL schema extension with common/shop/admin split
- [ ] Plugin class with `@VendurePlugin` decorator
- [ ] Plugin registered in `vendure-config.ts`
- [ ] Migration generated and run
- [ ] Types added to codegen by running the server and regenerating
